Original: This comes from the Outland Count.
He has a special request for the
[Guild] Guild.
[Page]
He apparently wants you to go to the
South Sanctuary. He has summoned you
to the Grand Court for more details.
[Page]
I shall await your swift return.
Be careful as you go.
Translation: This comes from the Outland Count.

[Guild] Guild.
[Page]

South Sanctuary. He has summoned you

[Page]
I shall await your swift return.
Be careful as you go.

Original: Gracious, you are a shambles...
Was the Outland Count's request so
troublesome?
[Page]
But you do appear to have completed
it. He came here every day until you
accepted his request.
[Page]
He was very persistent in asking if
[Guild] had been here. He appears to
be very reliant upon you.
[Page]
Now then, I again thank you for your
hard work. Here is the Count's reward.
As you would expect, it is luxurious.
Translation: Gracious, you are a shambles...
Was the Outland Count's request so
troublesome?
[Page]

[Page]

[Guild] had been here. He appears to
be very reliant upon you.
[Page]
Now then, I again thank you for your
hard work. Here is the Count's reward.
As you would expect, it is luxurious.

Original: Ah, hello! So you accepted my request.
Wonderful! The reward will be very
much worth your effort!
[Page]
Here is the problem. When we went to
the [Color:5]South Sanctuary[Color:0] for the summit,
I dropped my favorite cufflinks.
[Page]
They are very important and absolutely
irreplaceable. I want you to retrieve
them for me. How does that sound?
[Page]
I will be counting on you!
Translation: Ah, hello! So you accepted my request.
Wonderful! The reward will be very
much worth your effort!
[Page]

[Page]

[Page]
I will be counting on you!

Original: The cufflinks in question should be at
the [Color:5]South Sanctuary[Color:0], where the summit
took place. I will be counting on you!
Translation: The cufflinks in question should be at
the [Color:5]South Sanctuary[Color:0], where the summit
took place. I will be counting on you!

Original: Ah, there you are! The wait was
making me anxious! Did you find
the cufflinks!?
[Page]
Hmm... yes, these are them. A beast
had them, you say? Well, I am glad
you managed to wrest them back.
[Page]
Oh, you saw the inscription? These
were actually a gift from my late wife
on the anniversary of our wedding...
[Page]
It was the last thing she ever gave
me. I may be wealthy, but some things
in this world, money cannot buy.
[Page]
But thank you for your efforts on my
behalf! Your reward will be waiting
for you at the Dancing Peacock.
Translation: Ah, there you are! The wait was
making me anxious! Did you find
the cufflinks!?

[Page]

behalf! Your reward will be waiting
for you at the Dancing Peacock.

Original: Having accepted the Outland Count's
request, you arrive at the site where
the summit was held.
[Page]
The wooden cufflinks are lying in
plain sight in the middle of the room.
[Page]
But when you reach for them, they
suddenly float upward before flying
through the door behind you!

of events, you decide to chase after
the cufflinks.
Translation: Befuddled though you are by this turn
of events, you decide to chase after
the cufflinks.

Original: You pursue the cufflinks through the
door, only to see them already leaving
through another door!
Translation: You pursue the cufflinks through the
door, only to see them already leaving

Original: You decide to chase after the
cufflinks...
Translation: You decide to chase after the
cufflinks...

Original: When you open the door, you see the
cufflinks going straight down the

[Page]
You give chase, careful not to come
into contact with any beasts that
wander the area!

Original: You chase the cufflinks into a small

[Page]

Original: You move through the hidden passage

Original: You reach out to the cufflinks but

Original: It is then that you find the floating

[Page]

disguise and appear before you!
[Page]
Knowing its trick now, you should have
nothing to fear. Take up your weapons
and fight!
